                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="py-5 px-6 text-center tracking-wide">
                    <div class="posts">
                        <p class="text-sm">Use our tool to create a simulated scenario by drawing on a grid.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>

            <div id="capture-card">
                <style>
                button {
                background-color: #6617cb;
                background-image: linear-gradient(315deg, #6617cb 0%, #cb218e 74%);
